Show HN: Simple OpenAI Library with Caching
text:
I found a lot of my experiments / tests ended up calling the OpenAI API service with the same content over and over again, which can be time consuming - particularly for longer completions.

This is a very simple thing but if you need something like this in your C# project and don't feel like building it yourself, you may find it useful. This library also doesn't have any dependencies which is kind of nice imo.

Tell HN: Buy a CO2 monitor (not necessarily just a CO monitor)
text: It's simply insane just how much high CO2 levels effect our brain's efficacy. I recently bought one and it's night and day. I thought it was weird why I was having headaches until I saw that my CO2 monitor was reporting something like 10,000 ppm which apparently reduces brain function by more than 15%.
